## Sass Variables **Scope**
No **DOM** Awareness

```scss
.example { $columns: 2; }
.nested-class { /* $columns == undefined */ }
```

<!-- slide -->

## CSS Variables **Inherit**
**DOM** Awareness!

```scss
.example { --columns: 2; }
.nested-class { /* var(--columns) == 2 */ }
```

<!-- slide -->


```scss
@media (min-width: 30em) {
  .example {
    $columns: 6; /* üëé {} scope only */
    --columns: 6; /* üëç 30em+ browsers! */
  }
}
```

<!-- slide -->

