## New Old **Grid System**?
I'm not sure there's any reason to do this exactly...

```css
html {
  --columns: 12;
}

[data-span] {
  --width: calc(var(--span) / var(--columns) * 100%);
  width: var(--width, initial);
}
```

<!-- slide -->

```css
[data-span='3'] {
  --span: 3;
}

[data-span='half'] {
  --span: calc(var(--columns) / 2);
}
```

