## **Content** Requires **Quoted Values**

```css
div::after {
  --string: 'hello world';
  content: var(--string);
}
```

<!-- slide -->

## Content **Hack** For Numbers

```css
div::after {
  --number: 3;
  counter-reset: number var(--number);
  content: counter(number);
}
```

